            Chess Stats
        </h4>
      </div>
      <p id="tools">
        Javascript, D3.js, AngularJS, CSS
      </p>
      <p>
        Chess Stats gives Chess.com users insight into their playing history.
        Players can view their rating history and select past
        games for analysis. Users can perform statistical analysis
        where games are grouped by their openings.
      </p>
      <p>
        I developed the front-end and designed the look and feel of
        the site. <a href="https://github.com/ivanmalison"
        target="_blank">Ivan Malison</a> masterminded the back-end
